## Installation ##
Install the following gems:
	serialport	http://github.com/toholio/ruby-serialport

And for running tests:
	rspec
	rr


## Usage ##
port = '/dev/tty.usbserial-A7006AkP' # Depending on what port your device is connected to
arduino = Arduino.new :port => port, :read => { |in| puts "From Arduino: #{in}" }
arduino.write("hello")